snippet.title: The Fog Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Fog Official Trailer

Available on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.YourCompany.TheFog

You discovered a strange place in the woods and decide to explore it. But beware, a terrifying monster roams the forest, always on the hunt. Your mission: gather 12 keys to unlock the nearby cabin and escape the creature.

Music: A Thing In A Town.mp3 by SoundFlakes -- https://freesound.org/s/502704/ -- License: Attribution 4.0

#TheFog #TheFogOfficialTrailer
